snippet.title: Worship Kickstarter Trailer
snippet.description:
Kickstarter Campaign is now live !! 💚
https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/chasingratsgames/worship

Worship Kickstarter launch trailer. Blindly serve a dreadful god and lead its cult in a fresh multiplayer take on the roguelike genre inspired by Pikmin. 🔪🩸

Worship Kickstarter Campaign Video 🦵
https://youtu.be/1RpPid5MLSY

Worship: Blasphemous Prelude - Soundtrack 🎵
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=L1lA7...​
